{"id":"47935f8a-3163-4c00-8bde-a00722c15f59","title":"1557/02/13: To Lionardo di Buonarroto Simoni","type":"main-list-block","children":[{"id":"4b074846-8cc2-47c6-9624-b32d424117d3","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"From Rome, February 13th, 1557.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"17613592-df40-4801-8777-d761f2e3856d","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":3,"value":"8532f2fa-b614-4eed-9eae-586327f6a15a","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"c713d138-65ca-4656-9802-55efca05a36c","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":5,"end":8,"value":"501a8a32-2c8a-4934-9060-8c7e36339f0f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"52f0b617-3a8c-4ffe-b34c-5f422fc76a01","type":"codex/time-reference","start":11,"end":29,"value":"f4212ee7-57ce-4fd0-b729-840afa5ba074","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"69bcb9ee-430f-4ca7-b700-4b3168f149cd","type":"style/superscript","start":22,"end":23,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"0f4a8d5a-aff7-4e71-ab55-53a54a5fbb6e","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"To Lionardo di Buonarroto Simoni,","standoffProperties":[{"id":"5efe67a0-2df6-449c-9585-db8c8369a98a","type":"style/italics","start":0,"end":31,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"2a6c41ce-767a-4bb4-8562-e4efd79e4626","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":31,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"2654218e-065f-49e9-ba38-251e60b4c666","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"in Florence.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"756bf6c4-03c4-4efc-b7e3-922b8486ddae","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":1,"value":"0c663cc2-dd9f-40ce-b17b-734e41b369ef","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"4141fe9d-0728-47ec-92c5-b5c188ecf8af","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":10,"value":"671ee7e7-ae1b-4a5a-9591-b40203d5108f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"fc3f38f7-7757-4a88-9f73-c65ef8abed45","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"1b384982-04b4-457d-919e-7d91714eea7b","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"When, about two years ago, Messer Lionardo, a servitor of the Duke of Florence, came to visit me\u00A0here in Rome, he told me His Lordship would have been greatly pleased if I had then returned to Florence, and held out many inducements in the name of the Duke. I replied that I begged His Lordship to grant me sufficient time to enable me to\u00A0leave the fabric of St. Peter\u0027s in such a condition that\u00A0it could not be altered by the substitution of any other design for my own. As I heard nothing more about the\u00A0matter I proceeded with the said work, but it has not\u00A0yet reached the desired condition; and not only that, but I am obliged now to construct a large wooden model of the dome and lantern, so as to show the exact manner in which it is to be finished. All Rome has asked me to do this, the Most Reverend Cardinal di Carpi in especial, and I estimate that it will keep me in Rome for another year at least. I entreat the Duke, for the love of God and St. Peter, to grant me this delay so that I may come back to Florence freed\u00A0from this haunting thought, and feeling that I shall never be obliged to return to Rome again. With reference to the work having been stopped, this is\u00A0not true; for between stone-masons, bricklayers and labourers, there are still sixty men at work, as may\u00A0readily be seen, with good hope of continuing.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"7bee8e86-14a2-44ba-bec5-6a2151e4b44b","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":27,"end":41,"value":"3049f788-3eb2-49c3-b27e-c5cfe43bb1a2","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"11df3ba3-a77d-417d-9c27-6622f9274269","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":62,"end":77,"value":"ac52a90a-3e3e-4c05-ace5-5b6da5a37fec","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"2a0e67b3-724d-467e-bbd2-51aef62d642c","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":67,"end":68,"va